##Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for [ GTIL-Ahmedabad ] App
Company Name: Globe Textiles (India) Ltd.

Introduction:
This Privacy Policy describes how Globe Textiles (India) Ltd. we collects, uses, and discloses your information in connection with your use of our mobile application ("GTIL-Ahmedabad"), available on the Google Play Store.

Please note:
This App is intended for use by employees of Globe Textiles (India) Ltd. only. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect:
This App does not directly collect any personal information from you. However, it utilizes certain employee information already stored within our internal services for login and user-specific information access purposes. This information may include (but is not limited to):

Basic personal information:
UserName,UserCode, Job title, department, contact details (email, phone)

Use of Information:

The employee information used by the App is solely for:
User authentication:
Verifying your identity and granting access to the App.

Personal information access:
Enabling you to view your own employee information stored within our internal services.
We may use non-personal information collected from the App to:
i.Improve the App`s functionality and user experience.
ii.Generate statistics and analytics on App usage.
iii.Comply with applicable laws and regulations.

We do not:
i.Collect any additional personal information through the App.
ii.Share your employee information with any third parties without your consent, except as necessary to comply with legal obligations.

Data Security:
We maintain appropriate security measures to protect the employee information used by the App, including those implemented within our internal services. These measures aim to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of your data.

Employee Access and Control:
While the App doesn`t directly collect information, you have the opportunity to access and potentially update your employee information through our internal services. Please refer to your company`s internal procedures for details on accessing, updating, or deleting your employee data.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
